he following typesformats are supported: - Instances of Dependency. - String or CharSequence values, for example 'org.gradle:gradle-core:1.0'. - Maps, for example [group: 'org.gradle', name: 'gradle-core', version: '1.0']. - FileCollections, for example files('some.jar', 'someOther.jar'). - Projects, for example project(':some:project:path'). - ClassPathNotation, for example gradleApi().
